{
  "stem": "7598.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I got on very well with one cousin and not that well with the other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And obviously, the mother took the side of the daughter, and I, I felt neglected and unloved.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In fact, in retrospect, when I realized what my aunt did for two strangers, it was really quite remarkable.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I wasn't aware of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was only aware of the little bit of unfairness now and again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I missed my parents desperately.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Anyway, we were told to go to bed early.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But being very nosy, I heard some little goings on and I, I think I might have [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I knew that my uncle and aunt were packing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the next morning very early, we left for the station.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We each had a case.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And each, each child had a case.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went to the station where we must have met another 25 or 26 people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a passeur with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And another man who nobody quite knew who he was but we think he was-- so the head of the organization.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my young cousin who came with us said to my uncle, look, I'll come with you as far as Paris to help you and give you moral support.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I suppose for these younger people, it was an experience more than anything else.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I discussed this with my cousin last week.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We, the children, were carrying the diamonds in our [INAUDIBLE], not the parents.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And nobody was supposed to know about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But somehow, this man with a hat who seemed to be in charge of the escape route said to my cousin, well, if we have problems, we can always use the diamonds or something like that.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My cousin said you don't touch those children.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
